  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"template-hero resource-hero\">\n<div class=\"container template-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"template-hero-copy\"><span class=\"template-kicker\">RESOURCE CENTER</span><h1>制造知识、案例与资料</h1><p>精密零部件研发与生产全流程参考阵地。在这里你可以查阅加工工艺详解、材料性能参数、真实落地零部件案例，下载标准化工程资料。从零件设计 DFM 审查、工艺选型、材料比对，到报价沟通、出货验收，一站式获取工业制造参考信息，高效推进零部件项目落地。</p></div>\n<div class=\"template-hero-panel\"><img alt=\"制造资源指南\" src=\"/precision/insight-guide.jpg\"/><div class=\"template-panel-row\"><strong>Guides</strong><span>工艺与材料指南</span></div><div class=\"template-panel-row\"><strong>Cases</strong><span>行业应用案例</span></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section\" id=\"guides\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head\"><h2>资源分类</h2><p>覆盖工艺、材料、设计规范、常见问题和下载资料，支撑报价前的制造判断。</p></div>\n<div class=\"resource-grid\">\n<article><a href=\"/resources/material-handbook\"><img alt=\"材料指南\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/><div><span>GUIDE</span><h3>材料选择指南</h3><p>按强度、重量、耐腐蚀、成本和加工适配性筛选材料。</p></div></a></article>\n<article><a href=\"/resources/process-guide\"><img alt=\"工艺指南\" src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\"/><div><span>PROCESS</span><h3>工艺选择指南</h3><p>理解 CNC、3D 打印、钣金和常见后处理的适用边界。</p></div></a></article>\n<article id=\"cases\"><a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\"><img alt=\"设计规范\" src=\"/precision/case-medical.jpg\"/><div><span>SPEC</span><h3>设计规范</h3><p>精密零部件 DFM 可制造性准则，整理结构优化、公差标注、图纸规范要点，减少设计带来的加工难度与额外成本。</p></div></a></article>\n<article id=\"downloads\"><a href=\"/resources/downloads\"><img alt=\"新闻动态\" src=\"/precision/insight-knowledge.jpg\"/><div><span>UPDATE</span><h3>下载中心</h3><p>机加工工艺科普、新材料应用资讯、项目工艺复盘与平台最新内容更新。</p></div></a></article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section model-community-section\" id=\"model-community\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head model-community-head\">\n<div>\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">MODEL COMMUNITY</span>\n<h2>3D 模型社区</h2>\n<p>浏览、下载、分享适配 CNC 加工、3D 打印、钣金、注塑、铸造工艺的工业零部件 3D 模型库。平台兼容 STEP、IGES、STL、OBJ 等主流三维格式，可供研发工程师参考成熟零件结构、评估设计可制造性。你也可以上传自有三维模型，和行业从业者交流结构设计思路。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-community-actions\">\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/resources/model-center\">进入模型中心</a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/resources/model-center\">上传模型</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-filter-bar\">\n<div class=\"model-search\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></circle><path d=\"M20 20l-4.3-4.3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path></svg>\n<input aria-label=\"搜索模型\" placeholder=\"搜索模型、零件或工艺...\" type=\"text\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-filter-chips\">\n<button class=\"model-chip active\" data-filter=\"all\">全部</button>\n<button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"cnc\">CNC加工</button>\n<button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"3dprint\">3D打印</button>\n<button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"sheet\">钣金</button>\n<button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"injection\">注塑</button>\n<button class=\"model-chip\" data-filter=\"casting\">铸造</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-grid\">\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"cnc\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"精密轴类零件\" src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">STEP</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>精密轴类零件</h3>\n<p>适用于数控车削加工，含完整公差标注</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">CNC</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">不锈钢</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 1.2k</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"3dprint\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"法兰连接件\" src=\"/precision/product-flange.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">STL</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>法兰连接件</h3>\n<p>金属3D打印优化结构，轻量化设计</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">3D打印</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">钛合金</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 856</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"sheet\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"钣金支架\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">DXF</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>钣金支架</h3>\n<p>激光切割折弯工艺，含展开图</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">钣金</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">铝合金</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 2.1k</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"injection\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"注塑外壳\" src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">IGES</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>注塑外壳</h3>\n<p>ABS材质，含拔模斜度和分型线</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">注塑</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">ABS</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 643</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"cnc\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"传动轴\" src=\"/precision/product-shaft.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">STEP</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>传动轴</h3>\n<p>多台阶轴类，含键槽和螺纹特征</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">CNC</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">碳钢</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 987</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"3dprint\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"医疗器械支架\" src=\"/precision/case-medical.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">STL</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>医疗器械支架</h3>\n<p>微纳3D打印，生物相容性材料</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">3D打印</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">树脂</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 432</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"casting\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"阀体铸件\" src=\"/precision/service-finishing.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">STEP</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>阀体铸件</h3>\n<p>砂型铸造工艺，含浇冒口设计</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">铸造</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">铜合金</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 321</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"model-card\" data-category=\"cnc\">\n<div class=\"model-card-media\">\n<img alt=\"复杂腔体零件\" src=\"/precision/factory-floor.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"model-card-overlay\">\n<span class=\"model-format\">IGES</span>\n<button aria-label=\"收藏\" class=\"model-fav\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.18L12 21z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-card-body\">\n<h3>复杂腔体零件</h3>\n<p>五轴联动加工，含曲面特征</p>\n<div class=\"model-meta\">\n<span class=\"model-tag\">CNC</span>\n<span class=\"model-tag\">铝合金</span>\n<span class=\"model-downloads\">↓ 756</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"model-community-stats\">\n<div>\n<strong>12,580+</strong>\n<span>模型资源</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>8,200+</strong>\n<span>活跃用户</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>45,000+</strong>\n<span>月下载量</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>6</strong>\n<span>支持格式</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section process-guide-section\" id=\"process-guide\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">PROCESS GUIDE</span>\n<h2>工艺指南</h2>\n<p>汇集主流精密制造工艺知识库，面向研发、采购工程师提供选型参考。你可以快速了解每种加工方式适用零件形态、材料范围、精度上限、表面处理能力，在项目前期完成工艺对比，规避设计无法加工、成本超标、交付周期失控等问题。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-layout\">\n<aside class=\"process-guide-nav\">\n<h3>工艺目录</h3>\n<nav>\n<a class=\"active\" href=\"#cnc-guide\"><b>01</b><span>数控加工</span></a>\n<a href=\"#3dprint-guide\"><b>02</b><span>3D 打印</span></a>\n<a href=\"#sheet-guide\"><b>03</b><span>钣金加工</span></a>\n<a href=\"#injection-guide\"><b>04</b><span>注塑成型</span></a>\n<a href=\"#casting-guide\"><b>05</b><span>铸造工艺</span></a>\n<a href=\"#surface-guide\"><b>06</b><span>表面处理</span></a>\n</nav>\n</aside>\n<div class=\"process-guide-content\">\n<article class=\"process-guide-panel is-active\" id=\"cnc-guide\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n<img alt=\"数控加工\" src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 01</span>\n<h3>数控加工（CNC）</h3>\n<p>CNC 数控加工依靠数控程序驱动刀具完成材料去除加工，能够实现复杂型腔、异形曲面、高精度孔系结构成型，既支持单件样品试制、中小批量试产，也可承接稳定规模化量产，广泛应用于金属与高性能工程塑料精密零部件制造</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>适用材料</b>\n<p>铝合金、不锈钢、碳钢、铜合金、钛合金；POM、PEEK、尼龙、PC、亚克力等工程塑料。可依据零件载荷、使用环境、轻量化需求完成材质比对选型。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>精度范围</b>\n<p>常规量产加工精度 ±0.05mm；精密加工等级可达 ±0.01mm；超高精密定制加工最高可达 ±0.005mm。零件壁厚、结构形态、装夹方案都会影响最终可实现精度。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>表面粗糙度</b>\n<p>标准铣削表面 Ra 0.8–3.2μm；精加工可达到 Ra 0.4μm；搭配抛光工序可实现 Ra 0.2μm 镜面效果。粗糙度直接影响零件装配密封性、摩擦特性以及阳极氧化、电镀等后续表面处理效果。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>典型交期</b>\n<p>常规结构零件 3–7 天；多工序复杂异形零件 7–14 天；型腔模具、超高精密定制零部件 14–30 天，可根据订单排产协调交付计划。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n<h4>加工流程</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><div><strong>图纸审核</strong><span>梳理图纸尺寸基准、公差要求、装配工况，提前识别结构加工难点与设计风险。</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>工艺规划</strong><span>规划完整加工工序，选定适配刀具与工装方案，平衡零件加工成本、加工效率与成品质量。</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>编程仿真</strong><span>CAM 程序编写与路径仿真模拟，规避加工过切、撞刀风险，保障加工安全性。</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>首件试切</strong><span>试制首件完成全尺寸检测，确认尺寸精度、外观质量达标，固化稳定加工工艺。</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>批量生产</strong><span>量产阶段持续抽样检测，依托标准化过程管控，保障大批量零件尺寸一致性。</span></div></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/capabilities/process\">查看完整 CNC 指南 →</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"3dprint-guide\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n<img alt=\"3D打印\" src=\"/precision/product-flange.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 02</span>\n<h3>3D 打印</h3>\n<p>增材制造技术，通过逐层堆积材料成型复杂几何结构，适合快速原型和小批量定制。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>工艺类型</b>\n<p>SLA（光固化）、SLS（选择性激光烧结）、FDM（熔融沉积）、SLM（金属激光熔化）</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>精度范围</b>\n<p>SLA ±0.1mm，SLS ±0.2mm，FDM ±0.3mm，SLM ±0.05mm</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>层厚选择</b>\n<p>0.025mm（微纳级），0.05-0.1mm（精密级），0.2-0.3mm（标准级）</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\">\n<b>典型交期</b>\n<p>1-3 天（快速原型），3-7 天（功能件），7-14 天（金属件）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n<h4>打印流程</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><div><strong>模型准备</strong><span>STL 文件修复、壁厚检查和支撑添加</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>切片处理</strong><span>层厚、填充率和打印方向优化</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>打印监控</strong><span>实时温度、层间附着和变形控制</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>后处理</strong><span>去除支撑、表面打磨和热处理</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>质量检测</strong><span>尺寸扫描、密度测试和力学性能验证</span></div></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/capabilities/process/micro-3d\">查看完整 3D 打印指南 →</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"sheet-guide\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n<img alt=\"钣金加工\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 03</span>\n<h3>钣金加工</h3>\n<p>激光切割、数控折弯和冲压成型，适用于薄板金属件的高效生产。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>冷轧钢板、不锈钢板、铝板、铜板，厚度 0.5-6mm</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>精度范围</b><p>切割 ±0.1mm，折弯 ±0.2mm，孔位 ±0.05mm</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>表面处理</b><p>喷涂、电镀、阳极氧化、拉丝、钝化</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>2-5 天（简单件），5-10 天（复杂焊接件）</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n<h4>加工流程</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><div><strong>图纸审核</strong><span>确认展开尺寸、折弯顺序和公差要求</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>激光切割</strong><span>高精度切割下料，保证尺寸准确性</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>数控折弯</strong><span>按顺序折弯成型，控制回弹</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>焊接组装</strong><span>必要时进行点焊或弧焊</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>表面处理</strong><span>打磨、喷涂或电镀</span></div></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/capabilities/process/sheet-metal\">查看完整钣金指南 →</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"injection-guide\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n<img alt=\"注塑成型\" src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 04</span>\n<h3>注塑成型</h3>\n<p>热塑性塑料熔融高压注入模具型腔，适合大批量塑料零件生产。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>ABS、PP、PC、PA、POM、PEEK、TPE 等</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>精度范围</b><p>一般级 ±0.1mm，精密级 ±0.05mm，超精密级 ±0.02mm</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>模具寿命</b><p>10 万次（铝模），30-50 万次（钢模），100 万次（硬模）</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>7-14 天（手板），20-35 天（软模），35-60 天（硬模）</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n<h4>成型流程</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><div><strong>模具设计</strong><span>确定分型面、浇口位置和冷却系统</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>模具制造</strong><span>CNC加工、电火花和抛光</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>试模调整</strong><span>优化工艺参数，验证尺寸和外观</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>批量生产</strong><span>稳定工艺，控制周期和质量</span></div></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/capabilities/process/injection\">查看完整注塑指南 →</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"casting-guide\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n<img alt=\"铸造工艺\" src=\"/precision/service-finishing.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 05</span>\n<h3>铸造工艺</h3>\n<p>将熔融金属浇入铸型获得毛坯，适用于复杂形状和大型金属件。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>工艺类型</b><p>砂型铸造、熔模铸造、压铸、离心铸造、连续铸造</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>铸铁、铸钢、铝合金、铜合金、锌合金、镁合金</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>精度范围</b><p>CT7-CT9（砂铸），CT4-CT6（熔模），CT3-CT5（压铸）</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>15-30 天（砂铸），20-45 天（熔模），10-20 天（压铸）</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n<h4>铸造流程</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><div><strong>模具制作</strong><span>木模、金属模或蜡模制作</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>砂型/壳型</strong><span>造型、制芯和烘干</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>熔炼浇注</strong><span>金属熔化、精炼和浇铸</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>清理检验</strong><span>去除浇冒口、喷砂和无损检测</span></div></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/capabilities/process/polyurethane\">查看完整铸造指南 →</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"process-guide-panel\" id=\"surface-guide\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-header\">\n<img alt=\"表面处理\" src=\"/precision/product-shaft.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span class=\"process-guide-label\">PROCESS 06</span>\n<h3>表面处理</h3>\n<p>改善零件外观、耐腐蚀性和功能特性的后处理工艺。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-body\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-grid\">\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>适用材料</b><p>铝合金、不锈钢、碳钢、铜合金、钛合金、工程塑料</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>工艺类型</b><p>阳极氧化、电镀、喷涂、粉末喷涂、热处理、激光打标、抛光、钝化</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>膜厚范围</b><p>阳极氧化 5-25μm，电镀 3-50μm，喷涂 40-120μm</p></div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-card\"><b>典型交期</b><p>2-5 天（标准件），5-10 天（复杂件），7-14 天（特殊工艺）</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"process-guide-steps\">\n<h4>处理流程</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><div><strong>表面预处理</strong><span>脱脂、酸洗、研磨去除氧化层和杂质</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>工艺实施</strong><span>按选定工艺进行表面处理</span></div></li>\n<li><div><strong>质量检测</strong><span>膜厚、硬度、附着力和耐腐蚀性测试</span></div></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/capabilities/finish\">查看完整表面处理指南 →</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section resource-library\" id=\"material-handbook-preview\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"library-layout\">\n<article class=\"library-feature material-handbook-feature\">\n<div>\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">MATERIAL HANDBOOK</span>\n<h2>精密加工材料手册</h2>\n<p>\n            汇集机加工常用金属、工程塑料物性参数，结合 CNC、钣金、3D 打印、\n            注塑工艺特性对比选材方案，帮您精准匹配零部件工况需求，减少试错成本。\n          </p>\n</div>\n<a class=\"material-handbook-entry\" href=\"/resources/material-handbook\">\n<span>完整材料参数、加工建议、成本对比</span>\n<strong>\n            进入材料手册\n            <i aria-hidden=\"true\">→</i>\n</strong>\n</a>\n</article>\n<div class=\"library-list material-handbook-list\">\n<a aria-label=\"查看金属材料选型\" href=\"/resources/material-handbook\">\n<b>01</b>\n<div>\n<strong>金属材料选型</strong>\n<span>\n              收录铝合金、不锈钢、钛合金、铜材、碳钢等主流机加工金属牌号，\n              涵盖力学性能、耐温防腐特性、切削加工难易度，适配自动化、医疗、\n              航天零部件选材参考。\n            </span>\n</div>\n</a>\n<a aria-label=\"查看工程塑料选型\" href=\"/resources/material-handbook\">\n<b>02</b>\n<div>\n<strong>工程塑料选型</strong>\n<span>\n              汇总 PEEK、POM、尼龙、PC、亚克力等常用工程塑料参数，区分耐磨、\n              绝缘、耐高温、轻量化应用场景，提供 CNC 切削与成型加工注意要点。\n            </span>\n</div>\n</a>\n<a aria-label=\"查看材料工艺匹配指南\" href=\"/resources/material-handbook\">\n<b>03</b>\n<div>\n<strong>材料工艺匹配指南</strong>\n<span>\n              结合不同加工方式分析材料适配性，对比同种材料在 CNC 加工、钣金、\n              3D 打印工艺下的成型限制、表面处理能力与成本差异。\n            </span>\n</div>\n</a>\n<a aria-label=\"查看选材案例参考\" href=\"/resources/material-handbook\">\n<b>04</b>\n<div>\n<strong>选材案例参考</strong>\n<span>\n              精选各类零部件真实选材落地案例，对照使用环境、载荷需求复盘材料\n              取舍思路，为同类新项目提供成熟选材参考依据。\n            </span>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"material-handbook-note\">\n      如果您在材料选型、方案评估上存在疑问，可\n      <a href=\"/about#contact\">\n        联系工艺工程师\n      </a>\n      获取免费咨询。\n    </p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section design-standard-preview\" id=\"design-standards\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"design-standard-head\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">DESIGN GUIDELINES</span>\n<h2>精密零部件设计规范</h2>\n<p>\n          从工程图纸、尺寸公差、零件结构到不同制造工艺的设计边界，\n          提前识别影响加工成本、精度、质量与交付周期的关键设计问题。\n        </p>\n</div>\n<a class=\"resource-section-entry\" href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n        进入设计规范\n        <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"design-standard-grid\">\n<a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n<b>01</b>\n<h3>工程图纸与尺寸标注</h3>\n<p>\n          规范尺寸基准、视图表达、孔位、螺纹、表面粗糙度及技术要求，\n          减少图纸歧义和加工信息遗漏。\n        </p>\n<span>查看图纸规范 →</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n<b>02</b>\n<h3>公差与装配设计</h3>\n<p>\n          根据零件功能合理设置尺寸公差、形位公差和配合关系，\n          避免过度公差造成加工难度及成本增加。\n        </p>\n<span>查看公差规范 →</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n<b>03</b>\n<h3>制造工艺结构规范</h3>\n<p>\n          梳理 CNC、钣金、3D 打印和注塑工艺中的壁厚、圆角、深腔、\n          倒扣、折弯及支撑结构设计边界。\n        </p>\n<span>查看工艺规范 →</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n<b>04</b>\n<h3>DFM 检查与资料交付</h3>\n<p>\n          通过可制造性检查提前识别刀具可达性、装夹变形、薄壁风险、\n          加工基准及后处理余量等问题。\n        </p>\n<span>查看 DFM 指南 →</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section soft news-center-preview\" id=\"news\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"news-center-head\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">NEWS &amp; INSIGHTS</span>\n<h2>新闻动态中心</h2>\n<p>\n          关注精密制造技术、材料应用、行业趋势及平台动态，\n          获取与零部件研发、采购和项目交付相关的最新内容。\n        </p>\n</div>\n<a class=\"resource-section-entry\" href=\"/resources/news\">\n        进入新闻动态中心\n        <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"news-center-layout\">\n<a class=\"news-feature-card\" href=\"/resources/news\">\n<div class=\"news-feature-media\">\n<img alt=\"精密制造技术与行业动态\" src=\"/precision/insight-guide.jpg\"/>\n<span>专题推荐</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"news-feature-body\">\n<div class=\"news-card-meta\">\n<span>制造洞察</span>\n<b>FEATURED</b>\n</div>\n<h3>从零件设计到批量交付，如何降低精密加工项目风险？</h3>\n<p>\n            围绕材料选型、DFM 审查、工艺规划、首件验证与质量文件准备，\n            梳理影响零部件项目成本、精度和交期的关键环节。\n          </p>\n<strong>阅读全文 →</strong>\n</div>\n</a>\n<div class=\"news-side-list\">\n<a class=\"news-side-card\" href=\"/resources/news\">\n<img alt=\"金属与工程塑料材料选型\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>材料知识</span>\n<h3>金属与工程塑料选型时需要重点比较哪些参数？</h3>\n<p>从强度、重量、耐温、耐腐蚀和加工成本等维度进行材料比对。</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n<a class=\"news-side-card\" href=\"/resources/news\">\n<img alt=\"精密零部件质量管理\" src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>质量管理</span>\n<h3>首件检测和批量抽检分别解决哪些质量问题？</h3>\n<p>了解不同生产阶段的检测重点以及质量文件准备方式。</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n<a class=\"news-side-card\" href=\"/resources/news\">\n<img alt=\"智能制造与加工设备\" src=\"/precision/factory-floor.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>行业趋势</span>\n<h3>自动化设备零部件正在出现哪些结构和交付变化？</h3>\n<p>从复杂结构、小批量定制和高一致性需求观察制造趋势。</p>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"template-section soft resource-faq-preview\" id=\"help-faq\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"resource-faq-layout\">\n<article class=\"resource-faq-intro\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">HELP &amp; FAQ</span>\n<h2>帮助 FAQ</h2>\n<p>\n          汇总零部件报价、图纸准备、材料选型、工艺评估、质量验收及订单交付中的\n          常见问题，帮助研发与采购人员快速确认项目前期要求，减少重复沟通。\n        </p>\n<a class=\"resource-section-entry\" href=\"/resources/faq\">\n          查看全部常见问题\n          <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span>\n</a>\n</article>\n<div class=\"resource-faq-list\">\n<details class=\"resource-faq-item\" open=\"\">\n<summary>\n<b>01</b>\n<strong>提交报价前需要准备哪些资料？</strong>\n</summary>\n<p>\n            建议提供 3D 模型或二维工程图、材料要求、数量、表面处理方式、\n            关键尺寸公差以及零件使用场景。信息越完整，报价和工艺评估结果越准确。\n          </p>\n</details>\n<details class=\"resource-faq-item\">\n<summary>\n<b>02</b>\n<strong>不确定材料和加工工艺时怎么办？</strong>\n</summary>\n<p>\n            可提供零件载荷、工作温度、腐蚀环境、重量限制和预算要求，\n            工艺工程师将结合 CNC、钣金、3D 打印、注塑等方式协助完成方案比对。\n          </p>\n</details>\n<details class=\"resource-faq-item\">\n<summary>\n<b>03</b>\n<strong>是否支持样品试制和小批量生产？</strong>\n</summary>\n<p>\n            支持从单件样品、快速原型到中小批量试产及稳定量产。\n            可根据项目验证阶段调整加工方案、检测要求和交付节奏。\n          </p>\n</details>\n<details class=\"resource-faq-item\">\n<summary>\n<b>04</b>\n<strong>可以提供哪些质量与验收资料？</strong>\n</summary>\n<p>\n            可根据项目需求提供首件检测报告、尺寸检测记录、材料证明、\n            表面处理报告及其他约定的质量文件，具体内容以报价和订单要求为准。\n          </p>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"cta-band\">\n<div class=\"container cta-inner\">\n<div><h2>想要获取零部件设计与加工参考资料？</h2><p>查阅工艺参数、选材标准与 DFM 设计规范；上传图纸模型，同步获取精准加工报价。</p></div>\n<a class=\"light-btn\" href=\"/quote?mode=quickQuote#quote-upload\">立即报价</a>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
}
